rows.label: campfev11_3610_msg0004
rows.name:
With Iira in so much danger,
did it look like I was enjoying myself?

rows.label: campfev11_3610_msg0005
rows.name:
No, I wasn't trying to say
you were being disrespectful...

rows.label: campfev11_3610_msg0006
rows.name:
It's just that, thinking about your
restrictive life up until now, I thought
you were finally able to live freely.

rows.label: campfev11_3610_msg0007
rows.name:
I was sad about my mom, but so much
has been happening that I haven't
had time to really mourn...

rows.label: campfev11_3610_msg0008
rows.name:
And somehow,
I've ended up a knight of Iira...

rows.label: campfev11_3610_msg0009
rows.name:
I'm just doing my best
to get through each day.

rows.label: campfev11_3610_msg0011
rows.name:
If that's the case,
then I have to thank everyone.

rows.label: campfev11_3610_msg0014
rows.name:
In Iira—no, all of Alst—there are
people waiting who need our help
so much more.

rows.label: campfev11_3610_msg0016
rows.name: Laura, don't push yourself too hard.
